\]

\end_inset

in which, 
\begin_inset CommandInset nomenclature
LatexCommand nomenclature
symbol "$\\vec{b}$"
description "body force per unit volume"
literal "true"

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\vec{b}$
\end_inset

 is the vector of external body force per unit volume, 
\begin_inset CommandInset nomenclature
